          <tr>
            <td valign="top" class="texto2">
           <p>  <span lang="EN-US">As the President of <em>Interlitq</em>, I am delighted to welcome you to section 2 of Issue 13.</span> </p> 
          
           <p>With regard to new additions to <em>Interlitq's</em> editorial team, the Board of Editors would like to take this opportunity to welcome <a href="http://www.interlitq.org/staff/jeff_barry/bio.php" class="link1">Jeff Barry</a> as Deputy General Editor, and the Argentine writers <a href="http://www.interlitq.org/issue13-2/eugenio-conchez/bio.php" class="link1">Eugenio Conchez</a> and <a href="http://www.interlitq.org/issue10/patricia_delmar/bio.php" class="link1">Patricia Delmar</a> as Assistant Editors of the review.</p>
            <p>In terms of contributors to Issue 13, I hope that you will enjoy the evocative poetry of <a href="http://www.interlitq.org/issue13-2/andruetto/job.php" class="link1">Mar&iacute;a Teresa Andruetto</a>, <a class="link1" href="http://www.interlitq.org/issue13-2/eugenio-conchez/bio.php">Eugenio Conchez</a>, <a class="link1" href="http://www.interlitq.org/issue13-2/ruth-fogelman/job.php">Ruth Fogelman</a>, <a class="link1" href="http://www.interlitq.org/issue13-2/jennifer-hearn/job.php">Jennifer Hearn</a>, <a class="link1" href="http://www.interlitq.org/issue13-2/william-hershaw/job.php">William Hershaw</a>, <a class="link1" href="http://www.interlitq.org/issue13-2/alexander-hutchison/job.php">Alexander Hutchison</a>, <a href="http://www.interlitq.org/issue13-2/channah-magori/job.php" class="link1">Channah Magori</a>, <a href="http://www.interlitq.org/issue13-2/vasyl-makhno/job.php" class="link1">Vasyl Makhno</a>, <a href="http://www.interlitq.org/issue13-2/osip-mandelstam/job.php" class="link1">Osip Mandelstam</a>, <a href="http://www.interlitq.org/issue13-2/maria-negroni/job.php" class="link1">Mar&iacute;a Negroni</a>, <a href="http://www.interlitq.org/issue13-2/vasyl-makhno/job.php" class="link1">Orest Popovych</a>, <a href="http://www.interlitq.org/issue13-2/pauline-prior-pitt/job.php" class="link1">Pauline Prior-Pitt</a>, <a class="link1" href="http://www.interlitq.org/issue13-2/osip-mandelstam/job.php">Ian Probstein</a>, <a class="link1" href="http://www.interlitq.org/issue13-2/priya-sarukkai-chabria/job.php">Priya Sarukkai Chabria</a> and <a href="http://www.interlitq.org/issue13-2/p-scott-cunningham/job.php" class="link1">P. Scott Cunningham</a>; the wry and intelligent prose of <a href="http://www.interlitq.org/issue13-2/stephanie-johnson/job.php" class="link1">Stephanie Johnson</a>, <a href="http://www.interlitq.org/issue13-2/geraldine-maxwell/job.php" class="link1">Geraldine Maxwell</a> and <a href="http://www.interlitq.org/issue13-2/cynthia-rimsky/job.php" class="link1">Cynthia Rimsky</a>; and the lucid and magisterial criticism of <a href="http://www.interlitq.org/issue13-2/marcelo-cohen/job.php" class="link1">Marcelo Cohen</a>.</p>
              
               
            </td>
            
        </tbody>
      </table>
      </td>
      <td><img alt="" src="/images/issue_img/spacer.gif" border="0"
 height="219" width="1"></td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td colspan="4" rowspan="2" class="texto2" valign="top">
      
           <p>And all of these texts have been complemented perfectly by the vivid artwork of the leading Argentine artist <a href="http://www.interlitq.org/issue13-2/rodolfo-zagert/bio.php" class="link1">Rodolfo Zagert</a>.</p>
        <p>And, as you will note, Issue 13 also includes our "15 Miami poets" feature, showcasing the array of poetic talent, strong in both terms of craftsmanship and imaginative force, coming out of Miami, with contributions from <a href="http://interlitq.org/issue13/elisa-albo/job.php" class="link1">Elisa Albo</a>, <a href="http://interlitq.org/issue13/howard-camner/job.php" class="link1">Howard Camner</a>, <a href="http://interlitq.org/issue13/adrian-castro/job.php" class="link1">Adrian Castro</a>, <a href="http://interlitq.org/issue13/denise-duhamel/job.php" class="link1">Denise Duhamel</a>, <a href="http://interlitq.org/issue13/corey-ginsberg/job.php" class="link1">Corey Ginsburg</a>, <a href="http://interlitq.org/issue13/michael-hettich/job.php" class="link1">Michael Hettich</a>, <a href="http://interlitq.org/issue13/miriam-levine/job.php" class="link1">Miriam Levine</a>, <a href="http://interlitq.org/issue13/christopher-louvet/job.php" class="link1">Christopher Louvet</a>, <a href="http://interlitq.org/issue13/jesse-millner/job.php" class="link1">Jesse Millner</a>, <a href="http://interlitq.org/issue13/barbra-nightingale/job.php" class="link1">Barbra Nightingale</a>, <a href="http://interlitq.org/issue13/geoffrey-philp/job.php" class="link1">Geoffrey Philp</a>, <a href="http://interlitq.org/issue13/laura-richardson/job.php" class="link1">Laura Richardson</a>, <a href="http://interlitq.org/issue13/alexis-sellas/job.php" class="link1">Alexis Sellas</a>, <a href="http://interlitq.org/issue13/virgil-suarez/job.php" class="link1">Virgil Su&aacute;rez</a>, and <a href="http://interlitq.org/issue13/nick-vagnoni/job.php" class="link1">Nick Vagnoni</a>, and with all of these texts appearing alongside the artwork of the award-winning Miami artist <a href="http://interlitq.org/issue13/xavier-cortada/bio.php" class="link1">Xavier Cortada</a>. </p>
<p>I very much hope you will enjoy Issue 13 of <em>The International Literary Quarterly</em>, and that you will return to visit us many times in the future.</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>             
       
       <p><a class="link1" href="http://www.interlitq.org/staff/peter_robertson/bio.php">Peter Robertson</a></p>
 
      <p>&nbsp;</p>
                <p>&nbsp;</p>
                  <p>&nbsp;</p>
              <p><span class="titulo2"><a name="spanish">Estimado Invitado</a>,</span></p>
              
            <p>Como Presidente de <em>The International Literary Quarterly</em>, me es un placer darle la bienvenida al número 13 de la revista.</p>
            
<p>Respecto a las adiciones al equipo de redacción de <em>Interlitq</em>, el consejo editorial aprovecha esta oportunidad de introducirle  a <a href="http://www.interlitq.org/staff/jeff_barry/bio.php" class="link1">Jeff Barry</a>, ahora el Editor Asistente General de la revista y a los escritores argentinos <a href="http://www.interlitq.org/issue13-2/eugenio-conchez/bio.php" class="link1">Eugenio Conchez</a> y <a href="http://www.interlitq.org/issue10/patricia_delmar/bio.php" class="link1">Patricia Delmar</a> como Editores Asistentes.</p>
 
<p>En cuanto a las contribuciones a la edición 13, espero que disfrute de la poesía evocativa de <a href="http://www.interlitq.org/issue13-2/andruetto/job.php" class="link1">María Teresa Andruetto</a>, <a href="http://www.interlitq.org/issue13-2/eugenio-conchez/bio.php" class="link1">Eugenio Conchez</a>, <a href="http://www.interlitq.org/issue13-2/ruth-fogelman/job.php" class="link1">Ruth Fogelman</a>, <a href="http://www.interlitq.org/issue13-2/jennifer-hearn/job.php" class="link1">Jennifer Hearn</a>, <a href="http://www.interlitq.org/issue13-2/william-hershaw/job.php" class="link1">William Hershaw</a>, <a href="http://www.interlitq.org/issue13-2/alexander-hutchison/job.php" class="link1">Alexander Hutchison</a>, <a class="link1" href="http://www.interlitq.org/issue13-2/channah-magori/job.php">Channah Magori</a>, <a class="link1" href="http://www.interlitq.org/issue13-2/vasyl-makhno/job.php">Vasyl Makhno</a>, <a class="link1" href="http://www.interlitq.org/issue13-2/osip-mandelstam/job.php">Osip Mandelstam</a>, <a class="link1" href="http://www.interlitq.org/issue13-2/maria-negroni/job.php">María Negroni,</a> <a class="link1" href="http://www.interlitq.org/issue13-2/vasyl-makhno/job.php">Orest Popovych</a>, <a class="link1" href="http://www.interlitq.org/issue13-2/pauline-prior-pitt/job.php">Pauline Prior-Pitt</a>, <a class="link1" href="http://www.interlitq.org/issue13-2/osip-mandelstam/job.php">Ian Probstein</a>, <a class="link1" href="http://www.interlitq.org/issue13-2/priya-sarukkai-chabria/job.php">Priya Sarukkai Chabria</a> and <a class="link1" href="http://www.interlitq.org/issue13-2/p-scott-cunningham/job.php">P. Scott Cunningham</a>; la prosa inteligente y sutil de <a class="link1" href="http://www.interlitq.org/issue13-2/stephanie-johnson/job.php">Stephanie Johnson</a>, <a href="http://www.interlitq.org/issue13-2/geraldine-maxwell/job.php" class="link1">Geraldine Maxwell</a> y <a href="http://www.interlitq.org/issue13-2/cynthia-rimsky/job.php" class="link1">Cynthia Rimsky</a>; y la crítica lúcida de <a href="http://www.interlitq.org/issue13-2/marcelo-cohen/job.php" class="link1">Marcelo Cohen</a>.</p>

<p>Y todos estos textos van perfectamente complementados por las ilustraciones de <a href="http://www.interlitq.org/issue13-2/rodolfo-zagert/bio.php" class="link1">Rodolfo Zagert</a>, el artista argentino celebrado. </p>
<p>Y ejemplar 13 tambien alberga nuestro perfil literario "15 Miami Poetas", haciendo hincapié en el talento literaria considerable de las poetas de Miami: <a href="http://interlitq.org/issue13/elisa-albo/job.php" class="link1">Elisa Albo</a>, <a href="http://interlitq.org/issue13/howard-camner/job.php" class="link1">Howard Camner</a>, <a href="http://interlitq.org/issue13/adrian-castro/job.php" class="link1">Adrian Castro</a>, <a href="http://interlitq.org/issue13/denise-duhamel/job.php" class="link1">Denise Duhamel</a>, <a href="http://interlitq.org/issue13/corey-ginsberg/job.php" class="link1">Corey Ginsburg</a>, <a href="http://interlitq.org/issue13/michael-hettich/job.php" class="link1">Michael Hettich</a>, <a href="http://interlitq.org/issue13/miriam-levine/job.php" class="link1">Miriam Levine</a>, <a href="http://interlitq.org/issue13/christopher-louvet/job.php" class="link1">Christopher Louvet</a>, <a href="http://interlitq.org/issue13/jesse-millner/job.php" class="link1">Jesse Millner</a>, <a href="http://interlitq.org/issue13/barbra-nightingale/job.php" class="link1">Barbra Nightingale</a>, <a href="http://interlitq.org/issue13/geoffrey-philp/job.php" class="link1">Geoffrey Philp</a>, <a href="http://interlitq.org/issue13/laura-richardson/job.php" class="link1">Laura Richardson</a>, <a href="http://interlitq.org/issue13/alexis-sellas/job.php" class="link1">Alexis Sellas</a>, <a href="http://interlitq.org/issue13/virgil-suarez/job.php" class="link1">Virgil Su&aacute;rez</a>, and <a href="http://interlitq.org/issue13/nick-vagnoni/job.php" class="link1">Nick Vagnoni</a> con todos estos textos complementados por las ilustraciones evocativas de <a href="http://interlitq.org/issue13/xavier-cortada/bio.php" class="link1">Xavier Cortada</a>, el artista galardonado de Miami.</p>
<p>Espero que disfrute del número 13 de <em>The International Literary Quarterly</em>, y que vuelve a visitarnos muchas veces en el futuro.</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>             
       
       <p><a class="link1" href="http://www.interlitq.org/staff/peter_robertson/bio.php">Peter Robertson</a></p>
        
